<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="th">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Brinkshop - Official</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Mitr:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root{
/* ปรับเป็นโทนสีม่วงตามบรีฟ */
--bg:#F3E5F5;
--main:#9C27B0;
--dark:#6A1B9A;
--white:#FFFFFF;
--glow:rgba(156,39,176,0.3);
}
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;font-family:'Mitr',sans-serif;}
body{
background:var(--bg);
display:flex;
justify-content:center;
}
.container{
max-width:500px;
width:100%;
padding:20px 15px 40px;
}
.section{
background:var(--white);
border-radius:20px;
padding:25px 20px;
margin-bottom:20px;
box-shadow:0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
border:2px solid var(--main);
}
h1,h2,h3{color:var(--dark);}
.center{text-align:center;}
.logo{
width:150px;height:150px;
border-radius:50%;
overflow:hidden;
margin:0 auto 20px;
box-shadow:0 6px 20px var(--glow);
}
.logo img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;}
.badges{
display:flex;
flex-wrap:wrap;
justify-content:center;
gap:10px;
margin-bottom:20px;
}
.badge{
background:#fff;
padding:8px 16px;
border-radius:25px;
box-shadow:0 4px 10px var(--glow);
font-size:13px;
color:var(--dark);
}
.btn{
display:block;
text-align:center;
padding:14px;
border-radius:25px;
text-decoration:none;
margin-top:15px;
font-weight:500;
}
.btn-outline{
background:#fff;
border:2px dashed var(--main);
color:var(--dark);
}
.btn-main{
background:var(--main);
color:#fff;
}
.step{
display:flex;
align-items:center;
gap:12px;
margin-bottom:12px;
}
.step-num{
background:var(--main);
color:#fff;
width:26px;height:26px;
border-radius:50%;
display:flex;
align-items:center;
justify-content:center;
font-size:13px;
}
.price-row{
display:flex;
justify-content:space-between;
margin-bottom:10px;
background:#fdfaff;
padding:10px 15px;
border-radius:15px;
}
.price-tag{
background:var(--main);
color:#fff;
padding:3px 12px;
border-radius:20px;
font-size:14px;
}
.footer{
text-align:center;
margin-top:30px;
}
.socials{
display:flex;
gap:8px;
justify-content:center;
margin-top:15px;
}
.socials a{
flex:1;
max-width:100px;
text-align:center;
padding:8px;
border-radius:25px;
background:#fff;
text-decoration:none;
color:var(--dark);
font-size:13px;
border:1px solid #f3e5f5;
}
.small{font-size:12px;opacity:.7;margin-top:10px;}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
<div class="section center" style="border:none;box-shadow:none;background:transparent;">
<div class="logo">
<img src="https://drive.google.com/file/d/11kIbIhMHdOcCcb4y-fOHCD28v6Xrynns/view?usp=drivesdk" alt="Brinkshop Logo">
</div>
<h1>Brinkshop</h1>
<p style="color:var(--dark);opacity:.8;margin:10px 0 20px;">
Welcome To Brinkshop 🎀🥟
</p>
<div class="badges">
<div class="badge">🎨 รับทำป้าย</div>
<div class="badge">💎 โลโก้ร้าน</div>
<div class="badge">💧 ลายน้ำ</div>
</div>
<a href="#" class="btn btn-outline">
เช็คคิวงาน ✨
</a>
</div>
<div class="section">
<h2>📝 ขั้นตอนสั่งงาน</h2>
<div class="step"><div class="step-num">1</div><div>แจ้งประเภทงาน</div></div>
<div class="step"><div class="step-num">2</div><div>เลือกของตกแต่ง</div></div>
<div class="step"><div class="step-num">3</div><div>บรีฟงานละเอียด</div></div>
<div class="step"><div class="step-num">4</div><div>แจ้งอีเมลรับงาน</div></div>
<div class="step"><div class="step-num">5</div><div>ชำระเงินรอคิว</div></div>
<a href="#" class="btn btn-main">เลือกของตกแต่ง</a>
</div>
<div class="section">
<h2>💰 ราคางาน 🎀🥟</h2>
<div class="price-row"><span>โลโก้ร้าน</span><span class="price-tag">79–119฿</span></div>
<div class="price-row"><span>ลายน้ำ</span><span class="price-tag">49–69฿</span></div>
<div class="price-row"><span>แนวน่ารัก</span><span class="price-tag">69–129฿</span></div>
<a href="#" class="btn btn-main">เช็คราคาเพิ่มเติม</a>
</div>
<div class="footer">
<a href="#" class="btn btn-main">สนใจสั่งซื้อ/สอบถามทักไลน์เท่านั้นนะคับ 🎀</a>
<div class="socials">
<a href="#">Facebook</a>
<a href="#">Instagram</a>
<a href="#">LINE (mu)</a>
</div>
<p class="small">
© 2026 Brinkshop
</p>
</div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
